| Release PrintPDF
| 8 Nov 2007

Set Release$Source$Dir <Obey$Dir>
Set Release$Dir <Obey$Dir>.^.Release

| Update the application itself.

IfThere <Release$Dir>.!PrintPDF Then Wipe <Release$Dir>.!PrintPDF ~CFRV

Copy <Release$Source$Dir>.!PrintPDF <Release$Dir>.!PrintPDF ~CRV
WipeSVN <Release$Dir>.!PrintPDF

| Update the external ReadMe file.

Remove <Release$Dir>.ReadMe

TextMerge <Release$Dir>.ReadMe <Release$Source$Dir>.!PrintPDF.Resources.UK.HelpText <Release$Source$Dir>.Manual.Header 5

| Update the Source folder.

IfThere <Release$Dir>.Source Then Wipe <Release$Dir>.Source ~CFRV

CDir <Release$Dir>.Source

Copy <Release$Source$Dir>.c <Release$Dir>.Source.c ~CRV
Copy <Release$Source$Dir>.h <Release$Dir>.Source.h ~CRV
Copy <Release$Source$Dir>.Manual <Release$Dir>.Source.Manual ~CRV
Copy <Release$Source$Dir>.Make <Release$Dir>.Source.Make ~CV

Unset Release$Dir
Unset Release$Source$Dir